{"sentiment":0,"id": "4323802328130581", "bid": "H9ZcQy78p", "user_id": "3908702484", "screen_name": "小雨小于肖宇", "text": "今日最佳修图技术还是要更加精进拍照对于场景还有人物的构架也没有太大概念继续加油香港人也太多了叭", "article_url": "", "location": "", "at_users": "", "topics": "", "reposts_count": "0", "comments_count": "3", "attitudes_count": "3", "created_at": "2019-01-01 23:57", "source": "", "pics": ["https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/e8fa1114ly1fyrivcnwvjj22p721oe82.jpg", "https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/e8fa1114ly1fyrivkdbb9j232o21s4qr.jpg", "https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/e8fa1114ly1fyrivyyuvtj22oe21shdt.jpg", "https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/e8fa1114ly1fyriv94i9rj232o21se82.jpg", "https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/e8fa1114ly1fyriwzhs1pj232o21sqv7.jpg", "https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/e8fa1114ly1fyrixdnlk0j22u021ohdt.jpg", "https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/e8fa1114ly1fyriw7ioojj232o21s1kz.jpg", "https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/e8fa1114ly1fyrivunoryj232o21shdu.jpg", "https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/e8fa1114ly1fyriwd67lkj22gs21ohdt.jpg"], "video_url": "", "retweet_id": ""}
